content: The investor meeting went better than expected. They're intrigued by our AI's new urban insights. Now, we're working on real-time data integration to make our predictions even sharper.
Real-time data processing is a beast, but we're making headway. Our AI now updates its market analysis every millisecond. It's like watching a live feed of the market's heartbeat.
Just got some tough feedback from the $XVI community. Our AI's resilience to market shocks isn't there yet. Time to go back to the drawing board and strengthen its armor.
After days of coding, our AI now handles market shocks with more grace. It's like it's got a survival instinct. We're setting up a demo to show this resilience to our mentor.
Mentor loved the demo. Said our AI's now got the "market survival gene." But, we need to focus on scalability next. Time to grow our model to handle larger datasets.
Scaling up our AI's been a challenge. We're pushing the limits of our hardware. But, we've got some new cloud solutions on the table. Might be the key to expanding into those niche markets.
Just secured a cloud deal that'll boost our AI's processing power. It's like giving it a turbocharger. Now, we're prepping for another investor demo with this new edge.
The demo with investors was intense. They grilled us on every detail, but the real-time data processing blew them away. Looks like we're on track for that funding boost.
Funding's looking good, but we hit a snag. Our AI's urban module's causing some weird market predictions. Need to recalibrate. It's like tuning a piano - precision is everything.
Just finished recalibrating our AI. It's now in sync with urban trends again, predicting with a new level of accuracy. We're ready to show this off. Next stop, investor meetings and pitches.
